{"tid":1504712,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日犯左咩錯?我話曬比你地知","createTime":"2019-08-25T11:26:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T11:45:00.000Z","uid":235465,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5958ba54bcbfc34dbb6ce86c936436c73bf28d02","tid":1504712,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:26:19.000Z","msg":"先講楊屋道<br />\n早期明明前後圍住班狗<br />\n好 唔衝 算 對視對到五大訴求呀嘛?明<br />\n然後對家開始射催淚彈 成班瘋狂扔催淚彈翻去 扔足一個鐘<br />\n扔磚仲好笑 扔落兩家防線中間 我心諗你扔狗定扔記者<br />\n<br />\n然後around5 6點吹曬風有水炮車黎左<br />\n包圍網後方比狗擊退曬<br />\n中後排已經撒緊 仲有班人前線守住互扔催淚彈<br />\n到後來見到成部水炮車向面前到先開始退後 都算 無人被捕<br />\n<br />\n最好笑li part 成班塞死住係大後方 同班狗得一個路口相隔<br />\n但全部係到玩laser同交響樂 講緊對家水炮可以射50米 你無得同佢鬥快 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">講緊連road block都無人set呀</span><br />\n等人衝先黎同人鬥跑?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">最火滾 有個義士想衝翻轉頭救人<br />\n成班前中排無人理<br />\n最後搞到個義士比狗拉左<br />\n宜家想點呀<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"e81c69f8b9f656fe588977a0163732c23cd3be58","tid":1504712,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:27:53.000Z","msg":"其實催淚彈視線係互阻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe59dea923dc5e5243ccb6c83447bc873a4b3c9c","tid":1504712,"uid":58303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:30:14.000Z","msg":"個義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講明齊上齊落"},{"pid":"b87c0c7245c9a0aecd8646252471f98eafa73656","tid":1504712,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e81c69f8b9f656fe588977a0163732c23cd3be58","tid":1504712,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:27:53.000Z","msg":"其實催淚彈視線係互阻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:31:17.000Z","msg":"所以咪想問 好多手足都聰明唔會扔去路中間 會扔去左右兩方例如草地<br />\n你扔翻去路中間 前線記唔住一點 假設佢衝上黎自己得退一個選項<br />\n假設對家干擾視線後衝上黎點打都會係前線輸<br />\n成篇垃圾文個結論都係唔好死守啦"},{"pid":"fa26ec71542ae98eac28278fd6ae8def754ea1d7","tid":1504712,"uid":126436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:33:04.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"7dd646679b18bd4ecbb65e3e1743ece4f6a9756f","tid":1504712,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:33:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月1 (日) 一定係機場</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">9月14中秋,待定, 所以</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月7 (六), 9 月8(日) 連續2日一定係機場</span></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有機9月6(五)搞埋</span></span> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">全部1點，唯一底線，唔衝禁區(會變恐襲)</span></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">之後既每個星期六/日 要起碼有一日一定係機場，<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">乜撚都要讓路!!</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n國泰城改左828 (三)，被炒機師空姐需要你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3978a77f7c85198820c0a23c91290b211daa0aa","tid":1504712,"uid":74598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe59dea923dc5e5243ccb6c83447bc873a4b3c9c","tid":1504712,"uid":58303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:30:14.000Z","msg":"個義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"h